  "title": "Veterinary Nurse (Full-Time)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>For Animals Lovers</li>\n  <li>Manage reception desk and handle client queries.</li>\n  <li>Assisting the vets in their daily tasks, including during consultations.</li>\n  <li>Anaesthesia monitoring and assisting in surgery.</li>\n  <li>Hospital treatments and running laboratory tests.</li>\n  <li>Assisting in diagnostic imaging.</li>\n  <li>Perform relevant administrative duties.</li>\n  <li>Handling and upkeep of stock.</li>\n  <li>Help in maintaining cleanliness and hygiene in the clinic.</li>\n  <li>Diploma or Bachelor's Degree in Sciences such as Biology, Chemistry, BioTechnology, Veterinary Bioscience, or equivalent preferred.</li>\n  <li>At least 1 Year of experience working with animals preferred</li>\n  <li>Career path will include assuming a supervisory role in the clinic.</li>\n  <li>Must be compassionate towards and be willing to clean up after sick animals.</li>\n  <li>Will need to work on weekends - 4 days work week.</li>\n</ul>",
